The paper focuses on using reinforcement learning to develop a trading strategy for foreign exchange, which falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves optimization and decision control systems, which could fall under cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems). Finally, the paper deals with complex and random processes, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
